summary: Call for Competition for an new project!
descriptionHtml:
\"Dear, dear mother!
Send me a modder, who is able to create a mod, which allows me, to kill the Thalos Priest in Whiterun and all the people of Whiterun clap their hands, are happy and shout:
We have a new champion,
the Champion of Whiterun.\"
author: Everybody
